      h2 About me
      p I'm an experienced developer and technical leader, building on the web since 2006.
      p I’ve worked in both small and large technology teams, and have led the digtal transformation of multiple new and established businesses with pragmatic technological decision making.
      p I'm a creative engineer at heart, and I’m at my best getting hands-on in the teams I work with, talking to customers and iterating towards success. <a href="mailto:mike@mcarter.me">Email Me</a>.

    section
      h2 Work history
      p I’ve been working on the web in various guises since 2006, but here’s a summary of the past decade or so:

      .card
        .card__aside
          img.card__image(src="/assets/images/bitbrawn-logo.png", alt="Bitbrawn logo" width="80" height="74" loading="lazy")
        .card__content
          h3 BitBrawn <span class="card__dates">2021 - Present</span>
          p I’m growing BitBrawn, a web application studio that transforms businesses with brilliant software.
          p We offer web application development and consultancy, and focus primarily on SMEs looking to transform their businesses with bespoke web applications. <a href="https://bitbrawn.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Visit BitBrawn</a>.

      .card
        .card__aside
          img.card__image(src="/assets/images/logos/leaf.svg", alt="Leaf logo" width="80" height="48" loading="lazy")
        .card__content
          h3 Leaf <span class="card__dates">2016 - 2021</span>
          p I founded Leaf, a digital product agency, with my designer friend <a href="https://chrisannetts.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Chris Annetts</a>.
          p We grew the team to 7, and helped build brilliant digital products for several UK and US businesses. We shut down Leaf in 2021 to pursue other endeavours. <a href="https://weareleaf.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Visit Leaf</a>.

      .card.card--last
        .card__aside
          img.card__image(src="/assets/images/logos/holidayextras.svg", alt="Holiday Extras logo" width="80" height="80" loading="lazy")
        .card__content
          h3 Holiday Extras <span class="card__dates">2013 - 2016</span>
          p I joined Holiday Extras as a Web Developer in 2013, working primarily on their airport hotel and parking booking system.
          p During my employment I was promoted to Software Engineer, and then Software Architect, where I helped to technical decision making across the organisation. <a href="https://bitbrawn.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Visit Holiday Extras</a>.
